<header class="page-header">
  <h1 class="page-heading text-center">
    Fan Club
  </h1>
</header>

<p class="text-justify">This page lists a few things previous coworkers have said about me after working together. Most of these were left anonymously by managers, QA professionals, and software engineers as part of annual '360 survey' performance reviews. A few were taken from LinkedIn recommendations.</p>

<hr>

<ul class="references-list">
  <% for reference in @references %>
    <li id="reference_<%= reference.id %>">
      <%= reference.quote %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<% if admin? %>
  <footer>
    <span class="pull-right footer-links">
      <%= admin_link_to "Edit all", edit_multiple_references_path %>
    </span>
  </footer>
<% end %>
